Solar panel and propane heater?
Howdy,
I've been using a solar battery charger for a couple of years now, and
have been pleased with the results. I got a pretty cheap one, but
haven't had any problems with lack of charging ability or lack of power.
I would recommend using a deep-cycle battery in your Bus, but have used
the charger with a regular car battery. YMMV.
Good luck!
